TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION:
There are 4 separate queries [UNION ALL]. 1. T_CLAIM, T_CLAIM_ALV, T_CLAIM_QL - parameter $$NUM_DAYS - numbers to days from current day to pull batches. 2. T_CLAIM_EPS_MAIL - Is not partitioned on the source - hardcoded MIN and MAX batch dates. 3. T_CLAIM_RXA - Had to be separated out due to Historical batch loads on the source - added condition SYSDATE - 30. 4. T_CLAIM_AETNA - AETNA records needs to be pulled using a separate join. ITPR020090 Chnaged the SQ to read batches only for RECAP, MEDB and QL
--T_CLAIM_AETNA added on 12/10/2012 for APMCAS project --T_CLAIM_RUC added on 12/20/2012 for MEDICAL CLAIMS Project

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT /*+ ordered index(p x_batch_promo_pk) index(min_btch_dt x_batch_promo_pk) index(max_btch_dt x_batch_promo_pk) use_nl(REC_CNT) index( REC_CNT X_Batch_Qa_Msr_Comp_N01) use_nl(REC_CNT_OUT) index( REC_CNT_OUT X_Batch_Qa_Msr_Comp_N01) use_nl(REC_CNT_DELETE) index( REC_CNT_DELETE X_Batch_Qa_Msr_Comp_N01) use_nl(b) index(b x_batch_pk) */ p.batch_gid , min_btch_dt.batch_date min_batch_date , max_btch_dt.batch_date max_batch_date , p.tbl_nm ,b.feed_id, p.rec_chg_ts , (case when REC_CNT.qa_msr_val is null then 0 else REC_CNT.qa_msr_val end) + (case when REC_CNT_OUT.qa_msr_val is null then 0 else REC_CNT_OUT.qa_msr_val end) + (case when REC_CNT_DELETE.qa_msr_val is null then 0 else REC_CNT_DELETE.qa_msr_val end) BATCH_CNT from dwcorp.t_batch_promo p , (select qa_msr_val, qa_msr_code, batch_Gid from dwcorp.t_batch_qa_msr where qa_msr_code = 'REC_CNT') REC_CNT , (select qa_msr_val, qa_msr_code, batch_Gid from dwcorp.t_batch_qa_msr where qa_msr_code = 'REC_CNT_OUT') REC_CNT_OUT , (select qa_msr_val, qa_msr_code, batch_Gid from dwcorp.t_batch_qa_msr where qa_msr_code = 'REC_CNT_DELETE') REC_CNT_DELETE , (select qa_msr_val, qa_msr_code, batch_Gid, to_date(substr(qa_msr_val,5,4)||substr(qa_msr_val,1,4),'MMDDYYYY') batch_date from dwcorp.t_batch_qa_msr where qa_msr_code = 'MIN_BATCH_DATE') min_btch_dt , (select qa_msr_val, qa_msr_code, batch_Gid, to_date(substr(qa_msr_val,5,4)||substr(qa_msr_val,1,4),'MMDDYYYY') batch_date from dwcorp.t_batch_qa_msr where qa_msr_code = 'MAX_BATCH_DATE') max_btch_dt ,dwcorp.t_batch b where p.promo_stus_flg = 'Y' and p.rec_chg_ts >= SYSDATE - $$NUM_DAYS and p.tbl_nm in ( 'T_CLAIM_ALV','T_CLAIM_QL') and p.batch_gid = REC_CNT.batch_gid (+) and p.batch_gid = REC_CNT_OUT.batch_gid (+) and p.batch_gid = REC_CNT_DELETE.batch_gid(+) and p.batch_gid = min_btch_dt.batch_gid (+) and p.batch_gid = max_btch_dt.batch_gid (+) AND p.batch_gid = b.batch_gid UNION ALL select b.batch_gid , to_date('20010101','YYYYMMDD') min_batch_date , to_date('20301231','YYYYMMDD') max_batch_date , 'T_CLAIM_MEDB' tbl_nm , b.feed_id, b.batch_recpt_date rec_chg_ts , (case when REC_CNT.qa_msr_val is null then 0 else REC_CNT.qa_msr_val end) BATCH_CNT from (select qa_msr_val, qa_msr_code, batch_Gid from dwcorp.t_batch_qa_msr where qa_msr_code = 'REC_CNT_TCLAIM_MEDB') REC_CNT , dwcorp.t_batch b where b.batch_status = 'T' AND TRUNC (b.batch_recpt_date) >= SYSDATE - $$NUM_DAYS and b.feed_id = 'QL_RDT_DLY' and b.batch_gid = REC_CNT.batch_gid(+) ORDER by rec_chg_ts,tbl_nm,1,2,3
